thread.title: Red Geddes
thread.title_full: Mikes Dive Store reviewed by Red Geddes

author: Red Geddes
title: Red Geddes
text: As always with Mikes Dive Store the items I ordered turned up as quickly as postal services would allow and exactly as I wanted. Great shop with the added advantage of "Plankton points" which will save me even more in the future. Definitely ordering again and again. After having chance to read "diving in Ascension" will have better idea of anything extra I need for next trip!
